{"tid":1515734,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「突發」鍾健平被四名南亞裔男子以鐵桶襲擊 手部嚴重受傷】","createTime":"2019-08-29T09:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:30:10.000Z","uid":36714,"like":81,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":127,"replies":[{"pid":"90423990a66a32a28254e69e4e4d11c5cd1a289d","tid":1515734,"uid":36714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:44:01.000Z","msg":"TMHK<br />\n<br />\n【鍾健平接受本台訪問期間被四名南亞裔男子以鐵桶襲擊 手部嚴重受傷】<br />\n<br />\n「光復元朗」申請人鍾健平是日成功「踢保」後離開警署，在大埔太和路接受本台記者訪問期間，被四名南亞裔男子以鐵通及雨傘襲擊，記者隨即要求施襲者停止有關行為亦被襲，四人其後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者憶述當時正與鍾健平緩慢行走至太和站並進行採訪，期間發現被跟蹤，嘗試掉頭走時四名施襲者迎面而來，並推開記者，開始毆打鍾的行為，記者隨即以中英文表明身分，其中三名施襲者聽到記者身分後停手，惟仍有一人繼續向鍾施襲，記者其後嘗試分隔雙方，惟餘下一名施襲者不願停手，並開始毆打記者，四人約兩分鐘後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n記者其後立刻報警，約十名警員到場調查，由於鍾一直以雙手保護頭部，他的手臂嚴重受傷，而記者的口角亦被打破流血。<br />\n<br />\n本台強烈譴責有關暴力行為，並干預《基本法》第二十七條賦予市民的採訪自由，要求警方積極調查事件，並把施襲者緝拿歸案。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://wp.me/p5YkFQ-hKr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5YkFQ-hKr&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=ea4c7ca6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wp.me/p5YkFQ-hKr</a><br />\n<br />\n攝：Jeffrey Cheng<br />\n文：Kevin Li"},{"pid":"6ca6e4afce46c7aed93debccc1f7b589ad2e76cd","tid":1515734,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7VGF04.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7VGF04.gif&h=8d2b2993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=d6d5b20d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=bfd5e7a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=48d50a64\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"e8b6e449004a990e44d9f73c2ec8d1ab1def6ee6","tid":1515734,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUHazmx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUHazmx.jpg&h=3ccc6422&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3dd1af1a6b0c69e9b7e63b331a796172cd0f4e25","tid":1515734,"uid":36714,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"痴撚線！全民皆兵反暴力！"},{"pid":"603e0bc089a0ee5e2dd144bdc6a08f7d15754a70","tid":1515734,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c64ae2f7ef71f9a35e22505335ae5b11272e66","tid":1515734,"uid":36714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752ef362aafa9e27776be967d28c3a755fc4d169","tid":1515734,"uid":62167,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:46:18.000Z","msg":"警黑冶港"},{"pid":"dea7a222f5acb079a2c335acf7e894ee43642903","tid":1515734,"uid":36072,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"蝻亞狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a0a7b93a81e746afb3775c4afb43c2663f6978","tid":1515734,"uid":110043,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:46:48.000Z","msg":"警黑合作"},{"pid":"f55f47846951159af51c1a73bb85a0d67d48ff29","tid":1515734,"uid":96,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T